    "rule": "LLM loops are allowed against general machine-checkable criteria (diffs, diagnostics, coverage gaps, traceability gaps, stale evidence, assertions, and measurements). Intended behavior, oracle semantics, waivers, interface changes, performance tradeoffs, and signoff require human approval.",
